EN: The Army has made significant breakthroughs in military technology.

ZH: 这个国家新近升级了他们的陆军装备。
EN: This country recently upgraded their Army equipment.

ZH: 如果你想成为一名士兵，你必须服从陆军纪律。
EN: If you want to become a soldier, you must obey Army discipline.

ZH: 他从小就梦想成为一名陆军上将。
EN: He has dreamed of becoming an Army general since he was young.

ZH: 陆军与其他军事分支合作，形成整体的防御力量。
EN: The Army collaborates with other military branches to form a cohesive defense force.
